summary: A preset for my Breton character.
descriptionHtml:
[b]Once upon a time...[/b]

Mabrel Merowald is a young breton alchemist travelling across Skyrim and looking for rare plants, herbs and others magic ingredients.

[b]
Requirements
[/b]
You'll need [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7403/?]Lovely Hairstyles[/url] if you want her to look like on the screenshots.
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url], obviously.


[b]Installation

[/b]Just drop the file in [b][color=#f4f4f4]Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets [/color][/b]and load it ingame.
[b]
